OL,4,CMitholz - the tranquil Swiss village
OL,5,Cfacing a time bomb
OL,6, Mitholz, population just 170, is at
OL,7, first sight an idyllic place in
OL,8, Switzerland's beautiful Kander Valley.
OL,9, But its tragic history has come back to
OL,10, haunt it.
OL,12,FThe village's geranium-covered houses
OL,13,Fare traditional wooden farming chalets,
OL,14,Fmany still with living space for people
OL,15,Fupstairs, and stalls for farm animals
OL,16,Fbelow.
OL,18,FIt's a style seen all over the Alps,
OL,19,Fwith some houses 200 or 300 years old.
OL,20,FBut not in Mitholz. Here all the houses
OL,21,Fbear the same date: 1948.
